; Smooth multi-joint choreography for 2-joint arm
; Joint 1: unlimited rotation
; Joint 2: -90 to +90 limits

; === INITIALIZATION ===
G1 J1 A0 S120000
G1 J2 A0 S120000

; === PART 1: Individual joint sweeps ===

; Joint 1 slow sweep through 360°
G1 J1 A90 S80000
G1 J1 A180 S80000
G1 J1 A270 S80000
G1 J1 A360 S80000

; Return J1 to home
G1 J1 A0 S80000

; Joint 2 sweep within limits
G1 J2 A-90 S100000
G1 J2 A90 S100000
G1 J2 A0 S100000

; === PART 2: Coordinated smooth motions ===

; Slow synchronized orbit
G1 J1 A45 S60000
G1 J2 A45 S60000

G1 J1 A90 S60000
G1 J2 A-45 S60000

G1 J1 A135 S60000
G1 J2 A-90 S60000

G1 J1 A180 S60000
G1 J2 A-45 S60000

G1 J1 A225 S60000
G1 J2 A45 S60000

G1 J1 A270 S60000
G1 J2 A90 S60000

G1 J1 A315 S60000
G1 J2 A45 S60000

G1 J1 A360 S60000
G1 J2 A0 S60000

; === PART 3: Figure-8 pattern (J1 full rotation, J2 oscillates) ===

G1 J1 A10 S100000
G1 J2 A80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A40 S100000
G1 J2 A-80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A70 S100000
G1 J2 A80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A100 S100000
G1 J2 A-80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A130 S100000
G1 J2 A80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A160 S100000
G1 J2 A-80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A190 S100000
G1 J2 A80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A220 S100000
G1 J2 A-80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A250 S100000
G1 J2 A80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A280 S100000
G1 J2 A-80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A310 S100000
G1 J2 A80 S100000
DWELL 200

G1 J1 A340 S100000
G1 J2 A-80 S100000
DWELL 200

; === PART 4: Smooth final sequence ===

; Converge to center
G1 J1 A0 S120000
G1 J2 A0 S120000
DWELL 1000

; Brief pause, then spiral inward (slow)
G1 J1 A30 S50000
G1 J2 A60 S50000
DWELL 300

G1 J1 A60 S50000
G1 J2 A30 S50000
DWELL 300

G1 J1 A0 S50000
G1 J2 A0 S50000
DWELL 500

; === DONE ===
